</div></div></div>";s:14:"date_timestamp";i:1485437848;}i:1;a:8:{s:5:"title";s:18:"Festival 100+ Club";s:4:"link";s:50:"http://bollingtonfestival.org.uk/festival-100-club";s:11:"description";s:2600:"<div class="field field--name-field-image field--type-image field--label-hidden"><div class="field__items"><div class="field__item even"><img typeof="foaf:Image" src="http://bollingtonfestival.org.uk/sites/default/files/100%20Club%20logo.png" width="4048" height="992" alt="" /></div></div></div><div class="field field--name-title field--type-ds field--label-hidden"><div class="field__items"><div class="field__item even" property="dc:title"><h1 class="page-title">Festival 100+ Club</h1></div></div></div><div class="field field--name-field-main-text field--type-text-long field--label-hidden"><div class="field__items"><div class="field__item even"><p>A 100 Club is a monthly draw with generous cash prizes. The Bollington Festival 100+ Club gives 50% of the income each month back in <strong><em>three or more cash prizes.</em></strong> Some months there may be <strong><em>special prize bonuses.</em></strong></p>
<p>	The remaining 50% will go towards the money needed to stage Festival 2019.</p>
<p>	As the 100+ Club income increases each month, so the amount given in prize money and number of prizes will increase.</p>
<p>	You must be aged 16 or over to participate.</p>
<p>	You can pay as little as £1 per month (12 months minimum) for each ?chance?. You can buy up to 10 chances per month to increase your prospects of winning.</p>
<p>	Payment can be by cheque made payable to ?Bollington Festival 100 Club? or standing order.</p>
<h1>
	<a href="/ckfinder/userfiles/files/2019%20100%20Club%20Back%20Page%2017_10_16.pdf" target="_blank">DOWNLOAD AN APPLICATION FORM HERE</a></h1>
<p>	The draw will take place during the first week of every month. After each draw, the winning 100+ Club members will be sent a cheque as soon as possible and the winning numbers will be posted on the Festival website.</p>
<p>	The Bollington Festival 100+ Club promoter is Betsie Dixon (Bollington Festival 2019 Fundraising Coordinator).</p>
<p>	Winners may be asked for permission to publicise their participation and win in the Macclesfield Express, as well as online on social media platforms, but permission will always be sought before this happens.</p>
<p>	We will endeavour to contact all winners within 7 days of the draw by telephone, email or letter.</p>
<p>	Enquiries, cheques and completed application forms should be sent to:</p>
<p>	<strong><em>Bollington Festival 100+ Club</em></strong></p>
<p>	<strong><em>c/o 24 Birchway, </em></strong></p>
<p>	<strong><em>Bollington </em></strong></p>
<p>	<strong><em>Cheshire</em></strong></p>
<p>	<strong><em>SK10 5NA</em></strong></p>
